sa:palasha [Tree known as "flame of the forest"] = Butea Frondosa
sa:palasha -> he:plesheth [syrup the Pelasgis carried with them to Greece]
he:plesheth -> Palestine
sa:palasham [ancient name for Bihar in India]
sa:palasham ~ sa:palashkhanda [district of Bihar]
sa:palashkhanda -> gr:pelasgis [pre-Greek inhabitants of Greece]
gr:pelasgis -> Philistines
gr:pelasgis [later corrupted to "pala" and to "pale"]
